Show HN: Should I follow them on Twitter? – an app for the lols
text:
A demo application where you enter a Twitter username to see what they've been posting about lately, their tone and languages they use.

Built with Haystack: https://github.com/deepset-ai/haystack

It uses text-davinci-003 from OpenAI (for now) with a custom Haystack PromptTemplate.

You can check out the source code here too: https://github.com/TuanaCelik/should-i-follow

Show HN: Flasho- Omnichannel messaging using real-time database triggers
text:
Hi HN,

Flasho is an open-source, self-hosted tool to set up transactional SMSes and emails in minutes using database triggers. You just connect your database, set up notification triggers, create your email and connect to the service providers of your choice -- all from the dashboard without writing any code.

We currently have email and sms. In-app and push notifications coming soon. We currently support PosgreSQL. We'll be adding MySQL and MongoDB soon.

Looking forward to hearing your thoughts.
